TCH55 *
     C           KEY1      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           KTOKU   40       CUSTOMER CODE
     C                     KFLD           KNONY   40       DELIVERY CODE
      *
     C           KEY2      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           KTOKU
     C                     KFLD           KNONY
     C                     KFLD           INUKE
